[
  {
    "id": "20250213-01",
    "segments": [
      {
        "start_time": "0:01",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "This way, it's time for"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:07",
        "text": "News for kids, news"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:09",
        "end_time": "0:33",
        "text": "for"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:33",
        "end_time": "0:34",
        "text": "kids"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:34",
        "end_time": "0:41",
        "text": "但是你知道吗,每一年都有一百万棵树被砍下来做卫生纸。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:57",
        "end_time": "1:01",
        "text": "在肯亚,有一些人责自己做卫生纸。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:01",
        "end_time": "1:05",
        "text": "它们种植一种长得很快的植物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:05",
        "end_time": "1:08",
        "text": "这种植物有软软的叶子"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:08",
        "end_time": "1:10",
        "text": "叶子感觉很棒"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:11",
        "end_time": "1:13",
        "text": "啊,它们闻起来像柠檬"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:13",
        "end_time": "1:15",
        "text": "它们很强壮"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:15",
        "end_time": "1:19",
        "text": "而且它们大约是一个洗手间的大小"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:19",
        "end_time": "1:22",
        "text": "这种叶子很容易使用"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:22",
        "end_time": "1:25",
        "text": "这些叶子闻起来像柠檬"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:25",
        "end_time": "1:29",
        "text": "大小跟折起来的卫生纸一样大"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:29",
        "end_time": "1:31",
        "text": "而且不容易破掉"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:31",
        "end_time": "1:46",
        "text": "有人教导其他人种植这种植物,他们相信这"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:46",
        "end_time": "1:49",
        "text": "能帮助地球和树木。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:49",
        "end_time": "1:53",
        "text": "But in some places, people cannot grow the plant,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:54",
        "end_time": "1:59",
        "text": "these plants can start growing everywhere, they push out other plants."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:00",
        "end_time": "2:09",
        "text": "但在某一些地方,不能種植這種植物,這些植物會到處亂長,其他植物會沒有空間。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:10",
        "end_time": "2:14",
        "text": "Also, the leaves cannot go down the toilet,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:15",
        "end_time": "2:19",
        "text": "they have to be thrown away, or they can be put into the ground."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:19",
        "end_time": "2:27",
        "text": "而且這種衛生紙不能丟進馬桶,但可以買進土裡面,或是另外丟掉。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:31",
        "text": "But these people like growing their own toilet paper."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:31",
        "end_time": "2:34",
        "text": "They want to help trees and the earth."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:35",
        "end_time": "2:43",
        "text": "這些科尼亞人還是很喜歡自己種植衛生紙,因為他們想幫助地球和樹木。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:44",
        "end_time": "2:48",
        "text": "Do you want to try using these leaves as toilet paper?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:50",
        "end_time": "2:55",
        "text": "直接使用樹葉當作衛生紙,這是否是個好主意?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:55",
        "end_time": "2:57",
        "text": "植物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:57",
        "end_time": "3:00",
        "text": "You know, I've been thinking 我想了一陣子"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:00",
        "end_time": "3:06",
        "text": "We need to grow some plants in the garden 我們得在花園種些植物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:06",
        "end_time": "3:09",
        "text": "Maybe a tree 也許種一棵樹"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:09",
        "end_time": "3:11",
        "text": "Grow 生長"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:11",
        "end_time": "3:18",
        "text": "Trees are nice, but I once planted a tree 樹很好,但是我有一次種了一棵樹"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:18",
        "end_time": "3:23",
        "text": "And it grew too big 結果它長太大了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:23",
        "end_time": "3:29",
        "text": "We couldn't even see the house anymore 我們甚至看不到房子了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:29",
        "end_time": "3:31",
        "text": "Cut down 砍掉"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:31",
        "end_time": "3:34",
        "text": "So you cut it down 所以你就把它砍了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:34",
        "end_time": "3:38",
        "text": "Sure, we had to 當然 必須砍掉"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:38",
        "end_time": "3:44",
        "text": "Let's grow something that smells good like lavender 我們來種一些有香氣的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:44",
        "end_time": "3:46",
        "text": "比如說薰衣草"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:46",
        "end_time": "3:47",
        "text": "Lemon 檸檬"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:47",
        "end_time": "3:50",
        "text": "Oh, lavender is good"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:50",
        "end_time": "3:51",
        "text": "薰衣草很好"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:51",
        "end_time": "3:54",
        "text": "I can make lemon lavender cake"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:54",
        "end_time": "3:57",
        "text": "我可以做檸檬薰衣草蛋糕"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:57",
        "end_time": "3:59",
        "text": "今天的單字你記得嗎"
      },
      {
