  {
    "id": "20250214-01",
    "segments": [
      {
        "start_time": "0:01",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "This way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:06",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:10",
        "text": "真的假的!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:11",
        "end_time": "0:12",
        "text": "原來如此!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮室"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "ICRT's News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:20",
        "end_time": "0:21",
        "text": "It's Valentine's Day!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:22",
        "end_time": "0:26",
        "text": "Today, many people use dating apps to find love."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:26",
        "end_time": "0:30",
        "text": "But long ago, people met in other ways."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:31",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "今天是情人節"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:40",
        "text": "你们会不会好奇,四十年前没有交友软体,那时候的人怎么谈恋爱呢?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:40",
        "end_time": "0:43",
        "text": "Let's go back 40 years."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:44",
        "end_time": "0:46",
        "text": "A woman lives in Singapore."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:46",
        "end_time": "0:48",
        "text": "She likes swimming and traveling."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:49",
        "end_time": "0:52",
        "text": "She sends letters all over the world."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:52",
        "end_time": "1:01",
        "text": "四十年前,一个新加坡的女人很喜欢游泳跟旅行,还喜欢寄信给世界各地的人。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:01",
        "end_time": "1:06",
        "text": "A man lives in England, he likes trains and animals."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:07",
        "end_time": "1:08",
        "text": "One day he gets a letter."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:09",
        "end_time": "1:14",
        "text": "It's from Singapore, that's over 10,000 kilometers away."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:14",
        "end_time": "1:18",
        "text": "英国的一个男人喜欢火车跟动物。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:18",
        "end_time": "1:25",
        "text": "某一天,他收到了一封信,来自那位一万多公里外的新加坡女人。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:26",
        "end_time": "1:30",
        "text": "The letter is from the woman, he loves reading it."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:34",
        "end_time": "1:45",
        "text": "男人很喜欢这封信, 想要更认识寄信的女子, 所以他回信了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:52",
        "end_time": "1:59",
        "text": "两个人互相写了七年的信, 最后女人终于到英国, 想见这位男士"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:00",
        "end_time": "2:13",
        "text": "在機場見面"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:14",
        "end_time": "2:15",
        "text": "他們墜入愛河"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:15",
        "end_time": "2:18",
        "text": "一年後,男人飛到新加坡"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:18",
        "end_time": "2:20",
        "text": "跟女人求婚"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:20",
        "end_time": "2:22",
        "text": "現在,30年後"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:22",
        "end_time": "2:23",
        "text": "他們結婚"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:23",
        "end_time": "2:24",
        "text": "他們有三個孩子"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:24",
        "end_time": "2:26",
        "text": "他們做了一切"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:26",
        "end_time": "2:28",
        "text": "他們是最好的朋友"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:30",
        "text": "如今過了30年"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:30",
        "end_time": "2:31",
        "text": "他們在新加坡"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:31",
        "end_time": "2:36",
        "text": "他们已经结婚,并且有三个小孩,感情非常好。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:37",
        "end_time": "2:41",
        "text": "The woman and man lived 10,000 kilometers from each other,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:45",
        "text": "but letters of love made them close."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:45",
        "end_time": "2:50",
        "text": "这都是那一封封横跨地球的情书的功劳。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:51",
        "end_time": "2:52",
        "text": "Happy Valentine's Day everyone!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:53",
        "end_time": "2:54",
        "text": "Vocabulary"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:54",
        "end_time": "2:58",
        "text": "情人不远千里来相会,造就一段家话。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:58",
        "end_time": "2:59",
        "text": "Letter 信件"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:59",
        "end_time": "3:04",
        "text": "Tom broke up with his girlfriend over a line."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:04",
        "end_time": "3:07",
        "text": "湯姆用line跟他的女朋友分手了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:07",
        "end_time": "3:08",
        "text": "That's so rude!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:09",
        "end_time": "3:09",
        "text": "真没礼貌!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:10",
        "end_time": "3:12",
        "text": "He should at least write her a letter."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:12",
        "end_time": "3:14",
        "text": "他至少应该写封信给她。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:15",
        "end_time": "3:16",
        "text": "Write 写作。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:16",
        "end_time": "3:18",
        "text": "People don't do that anymore."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:19",
        "end_time": "3:20",
        "text": "大家已经不那样了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:20",
        "end_time": "3:21",
        "text": "I know."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:21",
        "end_time": "3:24",
        "text": "Maybe they find writing on paper hard."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:25",
        "end_time": "3:25",
        "text": "我知道。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:25",
        "end_time": "3:28",
        "text": "也许他们觉得在纸上写字很难。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:28",
        "end_time": "3:31",
        "text": "fall in love 坠入情网"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:31",
        "end_time": "3:34",
        "text": "my parents fell in love via letters"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:34",
        "end_time": "3:36",
        "text": "我爸妈因为写信而坠入爱河"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:38",
        "end_time": "3:41",
        "text": "how romantic 好浪漫"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:41",
        "end_time": "3:42",
        "text": "meet 会面"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:42",
        "end_time": "3:46",
        "text": "today people fall in love with their computers"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:46",
        "end_time": "3:49",
        "text": "现在人们跟电脑谈恋爱"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:49",
        "end_time": "3:52",
        "text": "or cell phones 或是手机"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:52",
        "end_time": "3:55",
        "text": "they even meet on cell phones, not face to face"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:55",
        "end_time": "4:00",
        "text": "他们甚至在手机上相见,而不是面对面。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:32",
        "end_time": "4:33",
        "text": "A."
      },
