      {
        "start_time": "0:13",
        "end_time": "0:14",
        "text": "是..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮是..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:17",
        "text": "我看到RT的..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:17",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "小孩的新聞!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:19",
        "end_time": "0:21",
        "text": "嗨,今天..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:22",
        "end_time": "0:24",
        "text": "你跟誰在聊?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:24",
        "end_time": "0:25",
        "text": "我的朋友!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:26",
        "end_time": "0:27",
        "text": "好,愛你!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:27",
        "end_time": "0:29",
        "text": "媽媽..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:29",
        "end_time": "0:30",
        "text": "好..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:30",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "今天..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:33",
        "text": "不要忘記清潔!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:33",
        "end_time": "0:35",
        "text": "不是現在,媽媽!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:36",
        "end_time": "0:38",
        "text": "This place is a mess."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:38",
        "end_time": "0:41",
        "text": "Maybe I'll clean up tomorrow."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:42",
        "end_time": "0:44",
        "text": "天啊,我媽媽讓我好尷尬。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:45",
        "end_time": "0:47",
        "text": "她不知道我在錄節目嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:47",
        "end_time": "0:49",
        "text": "A mom lives with her son."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:50",
        "end_time": "0:51",
        "text": "He likes comic books."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:52",
        "end_time": "0:54",
        "text": "He has lots of them."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:54",
        "end_time": "0:56",
        "text": "Many are old."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:56",
        "end_time": "1:01",
        "text": "有一個媽媽和非常愛看漫畫書的兒子住在一起。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:01",
        "end_time": "1:04",
        "text": "她兒子收藏了很多老漫畫書。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:04",
        "end_time": "1:05",
        "text": "兒"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:05",
        "end_time": "1:27",
        "text": "子"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:29",
        "end_time": "1:33",
        "text": "的漫畫書到處放,把家裡弄得一團亂。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:33",
        "end_time": "1:35",
        "text": "再加上台灣潮濕的天氣,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:35",
        "end_time": "1:42",
        "text": "天气让漫画书都发霉了,而且发出臭臭的味道。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:42",
        "end_time": "1:49",
        "text": "The mom asked her son to clean up again and again, but he didn't listen to her."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:49",
        "end_time": "1:51",
        "text": "She got angry,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:52",
        "end_time": "1:57",
        "text": "so she threw away some of his moldy old comic books."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:57",
        "end_time": "2:01",
        "text": "媽媽一直請兒子整理乾淨"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:01",
        "end_time": "2:07",
        "text": "媽媽一氣之下把發美的漫畫書都丟進了垃圾桶"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:07",
        "end_time": "2:23",
        "text": "兒子非常非常"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:23",
        "end_time": "2:24",
        "text": "生氣"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:24",
        "end_time": "2:27",
        "text": "他信愛的漫畫書有一些很稀有"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:27",
        "end_time": "2:31",
        "text": "可能再也沒辦法在樹墊裡找到"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:41",
        "end_time": "2:43",
        "text": "所以兒子報了警"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:43",
        "end_time": "2:47",
        "text": "結果現在媽媽必須賠償他五千元"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:55",
        "end_time": "2:59",
        "text": "媽媽扔掉了張希西的舊漫畫書"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:59",
        "end_time": "3:00",
        "text": "結果必須賠錢"
